{"tid":2163603,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"香港人要自保，同被制裁嘅人劃清界線","createTime":"2020-08-18T18:35:39.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-18T18:50:49.000Z","uid":284147,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"a37183984d003fc497c05619d631ea506dc4db51","tid":2163603,"uid":284147,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-18T18:35:39.000Z","msg":"如果銀行因為有11個人嘅戶口而俾美國制裁埋， 連累嘅係銀行其他無辜嘅客戶。<br />\n<br />\n影響到所有香港人嘅野，香港人有知情權，同必需<span class=\"xx-large\"><span class=\"blue\">自保</span></span>，同被制裁嘅人<span class=\"xx-large\"><span class=\"blue\">劃清界線</span></span>。香港人有權選擇唔同被美國制裁嘅人共用一間銀行，避免被波及，免受傷害。<br />\n<br />\n請<span class=\"xx-large\"><span class=\"blue\">所有銀行澄清</span></span>有冇同被制裁嘅人維持任何貨幣嘅客戶關係，令香港人可以選擇停泊資產係低風險銀行或金融機構自保，否則聰明嘅香港人會知道點樣<span class=\"blue\"><span class=\"xx-large\">避開高危嘅本地銀行！</span></span>"},{"pid":"d9727678d19d06ff396ccf57a2fdca9b6a363aba","tid":2163603,"uid":284147,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-18T18:36:02.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/abomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f1b59534d8182f76d5413b4f55ac32f880e6c8d9","tid":2163603,"uid":284147,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-18T18:37:06.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"973d436d1eb249ceb081eb396882ef84ff79743d","tid":2163603,"uid":100638,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-18T18:50:49.000Z","msg":"仲要所有銀行披露有冇留港元戶口<br />\n如果留住有被制裁人士港元戶口要即刻將資產轉移<br />\n否則好大機會成間銀行被制裁累埋其他人"}]}